== Hindi ==

=== Pronunciation ===
/ əi / or / ai / a long diphthong: approx. as ei in height 

=== Definition ===

A vowel of the [[Devanagari]] script. It's [[matra]], used to modify the inherent vowel in a consonant is written &#x0948;. For example the first consonant क with the matra looks like: कै.

